data.description: New HVAC system installed in August 2023! This home in Windchase is all about location. Close to the highway for an easy commute, close to schools and shopping. This single-family home  features a great floorplan perfect for entertaining. The open floor plan features a huge kitchen and a massive living room with another upstairs room that could be a second family room or bedroom. The downstairs features two bedrooms and a huge master bedroom and bathroom on the opposite side of the home, perfect for privacy. Two-car garage features built-in bench and shelving for the tinkerer. NO HOA. Updates include a new roof installed in October 2022. Refrigerator and doorbell camera can stay if buyer wants to offer on them. Buyer will need to buy a new survey.
